creator: Nomergy
descriptionHtml:
Want to look better, move better and feel better? Just grab a YBell. That's the key. It's all bundled into one - cardio, mobility and strengthening in 45 minutes.

Join now to receive FREE unlimited access to our YBell introductory workouts, plus -

• Community Forum where YBell users connect, ask questions and share experiences
• A single monthly subscription option providing full access to our exclusive YBell instructional videos -

A Beginners Program that builds the foundation of a simple, effective and sustainable training solution that will have you hooked and wanting more. 2 x YBell conditioning sessions, 1 Mobility and 1 Agility session every week for 4 weeks.

Push yourself with the Intermediate Program - consistency is key. 2 x Strength and Conditioning sessions, 1 Mobility and 1 Agility session every week will take you to the next level in your fitness journey.

A high intensity, challenging Advanced Program with the addition of gruelling animal ladders in Mobility and Agility sessions.

Subscription Terms and Pricing

YBell is free to download and for the you'll gain immediate access to 3 introductory workouts. There are YBell programs you can purchase as a single monthly subscription, paid in advance. Payment occurs via your Google Play account and the credit card linked to that account will be charged. Your subscription renews automatically unless it’s cancelled at least 24 hours prior to the end of the subscription period.

Subscriptions cannot be managed within the YBell app. They are managed in your Subscription Settings in Google Play after purchase. You can turn off the auto-renewal by cancelling the subscription in Subscription Settings. Once you purchase, refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term. Please read our full Terms of Use https://www.ybellfitness.com/privacy-policy/ and our Privacy Policy https://www.ybellfitness.com/privacy-policy/.

If you have further questions about our app, email us at hello@ybellfitness.com
